lead_paragraph: Jang Ha-na arrived back in Seoul on Monday after winning the HSBC Women's Champions event at the weekend but the South Korean golfer had to face some awkward questions over an incident that left rival Chun In-gee unable to compete in Singapore.

headline.print_headline: South Korean Jang Returns to Questions Over Rival's Injury
